Toni Edgar-Bruce https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toni_Edgar-Bruce 0 Toni Edgar-Bruce (4 June 1892 – 28 March 1966) was a British actress, frequently seen on stage. Her theatre work included the original West End production of Somerset Maugham's The Circle in 1921.
